description: I love Limbo parties, and this one is one of the best I've seen. You get a bunch of people with the need to party, and you get a super duper limbo contest. Everything started with the regular limbo that you and I know about, later was spin the bottle, and to make things more interesting, the next limbo was a string attached to two cocks and you had to Limbo under it. How awesome is that. Oh, did I mention that while all of this is going on, everybody is trying to find out if their friend Angel is gay or not. You gotta watch what happens at the end. Classic.
title: Tie It Up
